1. *Kuhinji* su neke od najčešće korišćenih prostorija u domu. (Kitchens are some of the most used rooms in a house.)

2. *Kuhinji* su dovoljno velike da se u njima smesti veliki broj ljudi. (The kitchens are large enough to accommodate a large number of people.)

3. U *kuhinji* se mogu kuhati zdrave i ukusne obroke. (Healthy and tasty meals can be cooked in the kitchen.)

4. Razni alati i uređaji mogu da se nađu u *kuhinji*. (Various tools and devices can be found in the kitchen.)

5. *Kuhinji* su uglavnom opremljeni modernim tehnologijama. (Kitchens are usually equipped with modern technologies.)